  "detailed_description": "In the only remaining human city of Bezoar, Major Fletcher, an Army Combat Veteran and soldier of the CLN, is dragged into a conflict between two of mankind's greatest enemies. He is to discover that nothing is what it seems to be.<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<strong>Hard Reset</strong> is an action-packed, single-player shooter for the PC. With over-the-top destruction, loads of enemies, great weapon variety and a beautifully realized cyberpunk setting, Hard Reset is sure to shake up the shooter scene.<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features:</h2>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A haunting cyberpunk / dark sci-fi setting<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Fast-paced, old-school shooter gameplay<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Hordes of enemies to destroy<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Epic boss fights <br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>A deep, experience-based weapon upgrade system<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>High-fidelity graphics with full dynamic lighting<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li><li>Extensive use of physics and dynamic environments<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li></ul>",
